description: Demolition of three existing warehouse buildings and construction of 7 blocks between 3 and 6 storeys high (max 21m AOD); containing 366 residential units (142x 1 bed, 113x 2 bed, 98x 3 bed and 13x 4 bed) and commercial floorspace for Class A1 (shops) / A3 (restaurant/cafes) / D1 (non-residential institutions / D2 (assembly and leisure)uses; with basement car parking, motorcycle and cycle storage, ancillary storage spaces and a new route through the site into Russia Dock Woodlands. New vehicle and pedestrian accesses to be created from Quebec Way
